## Usage with Claude Desktop

### local (no pypi needed)

if you haven't published to pypi, point claude desktop to your local project:

```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "{{ project_name }}": {
      "command": "uv",
      "args": [
        "run",
        "--directory",
        "/absolute/path/to/{{ project_name }}",
        "{{ project_name }}"
      ]
    }
  }
}
```

make sure you've run `uv sync` first!

### from pypi

if you've published to pypi:

```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "{{ project_name }}": {
      "command": "uvx",
      "args": ["{{ project_name }}"]
    }
  }
}
```

