- `get_bio()` - Get biography
- `get_contact()` - Get contact info
- `get_projects()` - Get projects
- `get_skills()` - Get skills
- `get_work()` - Get work history
- `search_info(query)` - Search across all resources
- `health_check()` - Check server status

## Available Prompts

